  "prompt": "Where can I see a Lamborghini in Bangalore?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, you can see a Lamborghini at several places, including:\n\n1. **Lamborghini Dealership**: Visit the official Lamborghini dealership in Bangalore. They often have models on display. The dealership is typically located in upscale areas.\n\n2. **Luxury Car Shows and Events**: Check for any luxury car exhibitions, auto shows, or automotive events happening in the city. These events often feature high-end cars including Lamborghinis.\n\n3. **Luxury Hotels and Clubs**: High-end hotels and exclusive clubs may have Lamborghinis parked in their premises, especially during weekends or special events.\n\n4. **Car Meetups**: Look for car enthusiast groups or meetups in the city. Enthusiasts occasionally showcase their luxury cars, including Lamborghinis.\n\n5. **Social Media and Local Car Enthusiast Groups**: Follow local automotive enthusiast groups on social media platforms. They often share locations where luxury cars are spotted.\n\nBy checking these venues, you should be able to find a Lamborghini in Bangalore.",
